    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "Do you get distracted when the badge on the Thunderbird icon appears informing you of new emails you received? Do you catch yourself immediately checking?\n\nWhatever reason you may have, if you want to stop the badge from showing up, this extension prevents the badge from appearing on the Thunderbird app icon in the Mac OSX dock completely. It will not appear anymore whenever you receive new emails.\n\nTo enable the badge again, simply disable this extension.\n\n<strong>To report any problems or issues, please do not use the reviews, but the provided support email (see on the right).</strong>"
    },
    "developer_comments": {
        "en-US": "Please let me know (by email is appreciated) if there is anything that can be improved or added to this add-on or if you encouter any bugs."
